metadata.name: Fast Food Elon
metadata.description: The Fast Food Elon is a collection of 6,969 unique  NFTs. Your Fast Food Elon   grants access to join only benefits, the first of which is access to holder campaign that will raffle every 69 minted (101times) until sold out. The winner will receive 0.69 ETH. For future benefits can you can visit www.FastFoodElon.com for more details.
